{"Sid":0,"Did":18047,"Id":"282361","Title":"羅東慶安宮繡旗","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collection/365c352c-0fc8-42b9-b29c-37e9a1d95aae/108-her-cw-1195-201910261942135db42861cfcbb0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n台灣傳統廟宇過去經常由地方人士或捐獻給廟方，可在廟會節慶遶境時展示。一般而言，繡旗上會繡有廟名、主神名，以及龍、鳳、獅、豹、虎、象等祥獸，或是八仙、八寶等。 　　羅東慶安宮正殿虎邊有一玻璃櫃中，展示了一方繡旗，長度約有6尺，採立式。繡旗上方為獅頭，額頭處向外突出，鼻口下有黑鬚。獅頭下方則繡有「羅東慶安宮　三聖尊王」等字樣，代表捐贈者所捐贈的廟宇；兩側各繡有一尾頭下尾上的龍，最下方則繡有寶塔。捐贈者是時任監察委員的博愛醫院創辦人許文政，地緣上也與慶安宮接近，雖宗教信仰不同，亦仍捐贈繡旗。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7702009","Keyword_Latitude":"24.6720481","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/522B3325-3305-43C5-9DA5-9A53CD5222BA","Original_Identifier":"282361","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"許文政 / 慶安宮 / 繡旗 / 羅東","dates":"創作時間 / 民國/戰後時期","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 19:55:53","Creator":"不詳","publisher":"","mediaType":"有形文物","language":"","timelines":"","city":"宜蘭縣羅東鎮","address":"中正南路175號","lng":"121.7702009","lat":"24.6720481","contributors":"","contributor":"林鴻文/ 蔡明志","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collectionOpen/22ad4406-8962-4fa0-b327-6b70213cfde3/108-her-cw-1195-re-201910261944225db42861cfcbb0.jpg"}}